data.description: Brick beauty shaded by mature live oak on tree-lined street filled with stately homes. Triple lot with parking for multiple cars. This house is too pretty to be believed, and you'll be amazed at all the ADA features and other wonderful touches too numerous to list - including a huge back yard with lap pool and large rear patio with canopied gazebo. (Patio is already plumbed for a hot tub!) Main house (approx. 2500 sf) has terrazzo flooring on first floor, with 4 upstairs bedrooms & 3 full baths including roll-in ADA bathroom with "smart toilet" on main level. 2-story guest house (approx. 900 sf) has kitchenette, laundry, bathroom with walk-in tub, built-in garden shed and huge light-filled upstairs bedroom, along with a brand new double mini-split A/C. Property has gated off-street parking, sprinkler system, & security system. Front door of the main house has optional auto-open function, along with a Ring doorbell. Versatile floor plan gives you the option of choosing which rooms to use as living, dining, office, or den areas. Huge Primary bedroom has 2 closets. Ample closets and storage throughout, including under the main staircase. Pool is 5 feet deep and equipped with grab bars. A pool lift chair can be included in the sale if desired. Wheelchair ramps will make your move-in easier, even if you don't intend to keep them! You will not find another house like this one! Close to Costco, convenient to I-10 and Earhart Blvd.
